{"tid":2059993,"cid":5,"subCid":11,"title":"香港警察急設新部門，並效忠中國","createTime":"2020-06-11T10:13:01.000Z","updateTime":"2020-06-12T07:32:35.000Z","uid":149978,"like":10,"dislike":27,"uniUserReply":39,"replies":[{"pid":"2acb714e2ab5cb5420ac89aa76932e22b068baae","tid":2059993,"uid":149978,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":2,"replyTime":"2020-06-11T10:13:01.000Z","msg":"針對中國在香港推動的國家安全法，香港保安局局長李家超在「南華早報」九日刊出的專訪中指出，<strong>香港警務處正在籌組專責單位負責執行國安法</strong>，職能包括情報蒐集、調查，<strong>並將與中國國安機構人員分享情報與資訊</strong>，這個新部門已經展開資源、人力調配等前期工作，<strong>將在國安法生效「第一天」立即上線運作。</strong><br />\n<br />\n<a href=\"https://news.ltn.com.tw/news/world/paper/1379044\" data-sr-url=\"https://r.lihkg.com/link?u=https%3A%2F%2Fnews.ltn.com.tw%2Fnews%2Fworld%2Fpaper%2F1379044&d=zXAIbGZ2Qohx5%2Bb7%2FAbjRDcZFjLth35g1vO%2BxS%2F2N%2Fg%3D&h=da2fdfeb\" data-ef-url=\"https://embed.lih.kg/frame?u=https%3A%2F%2Fnews.ltn.com.tw%2Fnews%2Fworld%2Fpaper%2F1379044&h=1982c492\" data-auto-link target=\"_blank\">https://news.ltn.com.tw/news/world/paper/1379044</a>"},{"pid":"cd102f78f2977dc3a5b1029cc8030402d0d5d85a","tid":2059993,"uid":28252,"like":28,"dislike":1,"score":27,"citedBy":2,"replyTime":"2020-06-11T10:14:11.000Z","msg":"終於可以老屈<br />\n既得利益者又贏"},{"pid":"ad9e40fb344295ca5f16cdc66437c035fd7cc67a","tid":2059993,"uid":28252,"like":7,"dislike":1,"score":6,"quote":{"pid":"cd102f78f2977dc3a5b1029cc8030402d0d5d85a","tid":2059993,"uid":28252,"like":28,"dislike":1,"score":27,"citedBy":2,"replyTime":"2020-06-11T10:14:11.000Z","msg":"終於可以老屈<br />\n既得利益者又贏"},"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2020-06-11T10:14:53.000Z","msg":"等飲三鹿奶粉"},{"pid":"9d2da92ffb9ee43790d0c9027dcb780e6b9451a3","tid":2059993,"uid":149978,"like":7,"dislike":1,"score":6,"quote":{"pid":"cd102f78f2977dc3a5b1029cc8030402d0d5d85a","tid":2059993,"uid":28252,"like":28,"dislike":1,"score":27,"citedBy":2,"replyTime":"2020-06-11T10:14:11.000Z","msg":"終於可以老屈<br />\n既得利益者又贏"},"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2020-06-11T10:17:59.000Z","msg":"好快無得上連登"},{"pid":"96fe78984eb3f8bd1e44a11a3f4b7e832